        <h1>Your Journey to a Sweeter Life</h1>

        <section id="track-meals">
            <p>Tracking your meals is crucial as it allows you to see exactly what you're eating and in what quantities. 
                This way, you can maintain a balanced diet, understand where you're consuming too many or too few calories, 
